{"tid":1600813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[929反赤納粹］81年前的今天- 張伯倫「慕尼黑協定」綏靖納粹德國","createTime":"2019-09-28T18:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T23:21:08.000Z","uid":101392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"984177db63f6c41afeafa0612b19007463737a73","tid":1600813,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:06:47.000Z","msg":"慕尼黑協定（英語：Munich Agreement；捷克語：Mnichovsk&aacute; zrada；德語：M&uuml;nchner Abkommen；1938年9月29日─9月30日）是英國、法國、德國、意大利四國首腦──張伯倫（首相）、達拉第（總理）、希特拉(元首/總統/總理)、墨索里尼(領袖)在德國的慕尼黑召開的會議。英法為避免戰爭爆發，簽署慕尼黑協定而犧牲捷克斯洛伐克的蘇台德地區，出賣了未在場的捷克斯洛伐克利益，是一項綏靖政策。<br />\n<br />\n1938年<span style=\"color: red;\">9月29日</span>，張伯倫第二次飛往德國。當日，在慕尼黑召開了由希特拉、墨索里尼、張伯倫、達拉第參加的德意英法四國首腦會議，規定把蘇台德區「轉讓」給德國。而割讓領土的捷克斯洛伐克，卻沒有權力出席會議。這就是著名的「慕尼黑協定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/慕尼黑協定\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E5%8D%94%E5%AE%9A&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=b696922f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/慕尼黑協定</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVCaUYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVCaUYi.jpg&h=6c609079&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"929b928d42c7b5c459717195dd5e55220b0fe34a","tid":1600813,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"今日中共以一帶一路經濟侵略歐美、剽竊知識產權、興建集中營囚禁維吾爾人、打壓香港人權<br />\n<br />\n國際社會必須反省81年前綏靖政策教訓，停止綏靖中共、容許中共坐大"},{"pid":"8c7e0c4974b5964f823643416407f351fb889e6a","tid":1600813,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"歷史在重演"},{"pid":"e8f1c2237488e15187d6ee6f442a258ac4a66b2c","tid":1600813,"uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"今日藍橋見到張banner講綏靖 用緊幕尼黑協定張相<br />\n冇人理....."},{"pid":"3c52002311fb3d2c29c5987ca94e56f46032ff12","tid":1600813,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f1c2237488e15187d6ee6f442a258ac4a66b2c","tid":1600813,"uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"今日藍橋見到張banner講綏靖 用緊幕尼黑協定張相<br />\n冇人理....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T22:56:54.000Z","msg":"有人理 <br />\ngphone有tweet<br />\n國際線好多like and rt<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1178282227588710400?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1178282227588710400%3Fs%3D21&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=50e79a10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1178282227588710400%3Fs%3D21&h=4491a575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1178282227588710400?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"8bb00de6a8aa0a54a6027640c3751b8e549ff88d","tid":1600813,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:21:08.000Z","msg":"臭猁狗張伯倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}